{
  "stem": "13313.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it's very hard to explain to people that haven't gone-- you know, 50 years later to be in exactly the same area.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And being then so self-conscious about his, his, his obvious conspicuous appearance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because it always ran through my mind that if he had, he had been alive then, if I'd been like that and raised like that, I wouldn't be alive today because there was no way you could escape the, the, the, the, the Holocaust if you were looking like that.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that always goes through my mind, even now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't mind him being ultra-Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't mind him observing everything, 100%.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I have very, very great strong feelings of anxiety about his, about his, about his, his appearance in, in, in a hostile world because what it could lead to.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's not rational, but that' just part of the after effect of what happened, you see?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You told me about another incident that happened outside the Toronto City Hall when there was a demonstration.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, about the-- oh, just a few years ago in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when we talk about how do I feel about the world and the issue, all-- so many years later, I'm, I'm an optimist, in terms of my initiatives.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I like to be a good father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a good son to my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I like to be a good husband.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I like to do all-- keep things in balance, treat all my fellow men well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when-- but when I see proliferation of, of, of swastikas and, and, and hate mongers and, and, and [INAUDIBLE] the [INAUDIBLE] and the [INAUDIBLE] and the-- and all these other people.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
